menu "breadboard: bb_task"

config BB_TASK_BASE_MAX
    int "Task base-registry capacity (max concurrently-tracked bb_task_create() tasks)"
    default 24
    range 1 64
    help
        Capacity of the pointer-keyed base registry that bb_task_create()
        upserts into (one entry per live task created through this API).
        Must be <= BB_REGISTRY_SNAPSHOT_MAX (64).

        Dormant in this PR -- no in-tree caller of bb_task_create() exists
        yet; a later PR migrates existing xTaskCreate* call sites onto this
        API.

endmenu
